snatcher
===

Snatcher is an IRC based torrent downloader

GOALS
- Be an automatic torrent downloader for power users, with straightforward configuration through TOML files

NON-GOALS
- Be an easy-to-use replacement for other downloaders with fancy features


Intalling
---

Assuming you have rust/cargo setup (e.g. via rustup: https://rustup.rs/)

Then install via cargo:

```
cargo install --git --locked https://github.com/ckcr4lyf/snatcher.git
```


